    relationship: "Materials science IS applied science: atomic bonding, forces, and classification"

  - id: ENGR-101
    relationship: "Engineering provides the design process; materials provide the physical vocabulary"

  - id: CHEM-101
    relationship: "Chemistry explains why materials have the properties they do"

  - id: MATH-101
    relationship: "Material properties are quantitative: force, stress, cost analysis"

  - id: TRADE-101
    relationship: "Every trade works with specific materials using specific processes"

